title: Niger Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Niger decreased to 1763500 XOF Million in August from 1777100 XOF Million in July of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Niger averaged 802773 XOF Million from 2004 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1778700 XOF Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 171030 XOF Million in February of 2004. This page provides - Niger Money Supply M2- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of West African States (BCEAO)
